  "0.52 × 10⁶": "",
  "4.52 × 10⁴": "",
  "452 × 10²": "",
  "In proper scientific notation, the coefficient must be between 1 and 10 (including 1 but not 10). Only 4.52 × 10⁴ has a coefficient in this range. The other options have coefficients that are too large or too small.": "",
  "What is 5,600,000 written in scientific notation?": "",
