  "It must be a number between 1 and 10": "",
  "It must always be exactly equal to one": "",
  "It must be less than one in all cases": "",
  "The coefficient in scientific notation must be greater than or equal to 1 and less than 10. This standardized form ensures that every number has one unique representation in scientific notation.": "",
